What does this component render when it first appears on screen?

```jsx
function Greeting() {
  const [name, setName] = useState('World');

  return (
    <div>
      <h1>Hello, {name}!</h1>
      <input
        value={name}
        onChange={(e) => setName(e.target.value)}
      />
    </div>
  );
}
```

A product manager reports: "The notification badge always shows 0 even after new notifications arrive." Look at this component. What is wrong?

